com.github.wuic.servlet

Class WuicServletContextListener.PropertiesWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.wuic.servlet.WuicServletContextListener.PropertiesWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BiFunction<String,String,String>
    Enclosing class:
    WuicServletContextListener

    public static final class WuicServletContextListener.PropertiesWrapper
extends Object
implements BiFunction<String,String,String>

    A properties that delegate call to a wrapped instance and modify the value associated to ApplicationConfig.WUIC_SERVLET_CONTEXT_PARAM to make sure it starts with the servlet context's path. If the value is null, then it tries first to retrieve a mapping from any installed WuicServlet. If no mapping can be retrieved, then the default value is applied.
